OL,3,CCouple claim incorrect passport rule
OL,4,Cleft them #4,000 out of pocket
OL,6,FA Guernsey man claims he and his wife
OL,7,Fhave been left more than #4,000 out of
OL,8,Fpocket after Swissport staff denied
OL,9,Fhim boarding at Jersey Airport.
OL,11,FGrant Hardy says they checked their
OL,12,Fdocuments were valid for their holiday
OL,13,Fto Tenerife, but he was refused travel
OL,14,Fdue to concerns over his passport's
OL,15,Fvalidity.
OL,17,FThey now want compensation for their
OL,18,Fholiday being ruined, but Jersey
OL,19,Fauthorities are adamant that check-in
OL,20,Fstaff followed the correct rules.
