OL,6,FGrant explains: "The rules aren't
OL,7,Fdifficult to interpret which makes it
OL,8,Feven more frustrating and they have
OL,9,Fbeen in place for some time, so I
OL,10,Fdon't see how anybody in a position of
OL,11,Fauthority, certainly who is in this
OL,12,Findustry, could have got those rules
OL,13,Fwrong.
OL,15,F"This is likely to affect other
OL,16,Fpeople. I know there were two other
OL,17,Fpassengers on the same flight as us
OL,18,Fand I would imagine there are many
OL,19,Fmore, so I think it needs to be fixed."
