OL,3,CCouple claim incorrect passport rule
OL,4,Cleft them #4,000 out of pocket
OL,6,FThe issue surrounds post-Brexit rules
OL,7,Ffor British passport holders entering
OL,8,Fthe Schengen Area - a European group
OL,9,Fof 29 member states including Spain.
OL,11,FTo enter, travellers must ensure their
OL,12,Fpassport was issued less than ten
OL,13,Fyears before the day they arrive in a
OL,14,FSchengen Area country. They also need
OL,15,Fat least three months remaining on the
OL,16,Fdocument on the day they are due to
OL,17,Fleave.
