OL,3,CCouple claim incorrect passport rule
OL,4,Cleft them #4,000 out of pocket
OL,6,FGrant and his wife tried to fly in
OL,7,FFebruary; his passport was issued in
OL,8,FMarch 2015 and he still had eight
OL,9,Fmonths before it expired, so it
OL,10,Fappears to have been valid.
OL,12,FThe confusion may have come from the
OL,13,Fso-called '10-year rule' as British
OL,14,Fpassport holders used to be able to
OL,15,Fcarry over up to nine months from an
OL,16,Fold passport to a new one.
OL,18,FThese can still be used, as long as
OL,19,Fthey meet all existing travel rules.
