OL,6,FSimon Calder, a travel expert who
OL,7,Ffights for consumer rights, says the
OL,8,Frules are still being wrongly applied
OL,9,Fby many officials and operators.
OL,11,FHe adds: "I haven't seen Grant's
OL,12,Fpassport but from the reports I've
OL,13,Fseen, he should have been allowed to
OL,14,Ftravel.
