OL,6,F"I went into great detail in 2021, as
OL,7,Fsoon as we left the European Union, to
OL,8,Ffind out exactly what the rules were.
OL,9,FI told all the big airlines, the
OL,10,FForeign Office, the holiday companies
OL,11,Fand four years on, they're still
OL,12,Fwrongly turning people away."
OL,14,FGrant is considering taking his case
OL,15,Fto a small claims court in Jersey.
